Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.29,0:00:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西嗎

Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子小姐  請收下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是念珠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是送給我的禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿錢來買
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強行推銷嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會幸福的哦
