Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在歐洲的食蟻獸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占卜嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴勃羅·畢卡索筆下的食蟻獸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我不會上當的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.64,0:00:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給你了
