Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉花為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:00:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞聞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  茉莉花的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.51,0:01:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提  這是我父親的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  茉莉花
