Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.02,0:01:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是神清氣爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也要孝敬一下父母嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給你  還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:01:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天國的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此後每天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子都要做噩夢
